Messages.Value: Thank you for calling Travel Agency, my name is Liam Johnson. How may I assist you today?
Hi Liam, my name is Sarah Smith and I'm calling regarding my upcoming trip from Los Angeles to New York City.
Sure thing, Sarah. What seems to be the issue?

Well, I just received my hotel reservation confirmation and the dates are incorrect. I booked the hotel from September 10th to 15th, but the confirmation says September 9th to 14th. Can you help me fix this?
I apologize for the inconvenience, Sarah. Let me check our records and see what can be done. Can you please provide me with your hotel name and reservation number?
Yes, it's the Marriott Marquis in Times Square and the reservation number is 1234567890.

Thank you, Sarah. I see that there was a mistake made by the hotel and they have already been contacted to fix the issue. However, as a precaution, I can make a note on your reservation and have a customer service representative follow up with you to make sure everything is corrected. Does that sound good?
Yes, that would be great. Thank you for your help, Liam.
You're welcome, Sarah. Is there anything else I can assist you with?
No, that's all. Thank you again.
